data.description: Beautiful home on corner lot in the heart of Wood Dale. Open floor plan features tons of natural light along with high vaulted ceilings!!  Must see this custom home!  Huge Chef's kitchen features tons of cabinet/counter space! 3 nicely sized bedrooms along with 2 full baths!  Partially finished lower level!  Huge garage has enough space for 3 cars plus tons of storage!!  Huge fenced in backyard great for all the dogs and summer BBQ's.  Close to tons of restaurants, shopping and expressways!
